      <p><b>Course description from student point of view:</b></p>
      <p>This course is for students without significant prior experience of DL.
        Thus, if you have prior experience and are looking for more of the
        theoretical background and advanced DL knowledge, this course is not
        recommended. The course is well rounded in terms of concepts. It helps
        us understand the fundamentals of Deep Learning.&nbsp; This course
        requires some basic knowledge and skills about coding.</p>
